Consider the following class definition. 
 public class Dog 
{
 private String name; 
 private int age; 

public String getName() 
 { 
 return name; 
 } 

public int getAge() 
 { 
 return age; 
 } 
}

The following segment appears in a class other than  Dog.
 Dog fido = new Dog(); 
System.out.print("name: " + fido.getName()); 
System.out.print(", age: " + fido.getAge());
